    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You have learned how to keep firearm siege engines ready for battle despite harrowing circumstances.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Siege Engineer, Knowledge (engineering) or Profession (siege engineer) 7 ranks, proficiency with at least one firearm siege engine.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You gain a +2 competence bonus on any Craft (siege engine) checks made to repair a firearm siege engine. In addition, if you are the crew leader for a firearm siege engine with the broken condition, that siege engine's misfire range is increased by only 2 instead of by 4, and the broken siege engine must misfire twice before it explodes.",
